WEBVTT

00:00.387 --> 00:04.252
It's a surreal scene here in downtown Boston along the marathon route.

00:04.409 --> 00:09.064
It's obvious that the thousands of spectators were terrified by the bomb blast.

00:09.383 --> 00:12.005
They left everything in place as they ran to safety.

00:12.412 --> 00:16.667
In that debris, you can find gloves, makeup, food, even blankets.

00:16.999 --> 00:21.219
The police had set up a wide perimeter in order to investigate this crime.

00:21.652 --> 00:26.375
Three people died including an 8-year-old boy, more than 140 are injured.

